<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">Please tell me this isn't true!  I got some tells by some people I was partying with the other night that Mages aren't really valuable in the upper levels...not like Clerics, Warriors, Enchanters...and it can be hard to find a group when you are are high in levels.<p>

Any truth to this Mages?  I mean I understand that everyone loves a Cleric who can heal their behind...or a Warrior to go toe-to-toe with mobs, but are Mages not 'liked'?<p>

Necros seem to be a dime a dozen these days...And enchanters are nice if you don't mind not doing a ton of direct damage even they are invaluable for the Clarity they give out...not to mention their crowd control abilities...<p>

I love my little elementals!  They are cute and never talk back!  They never complain about you looting too much...camping one site for too long...they dont even mind confronting a High Level Mob while you hightail it outta there!  ;)</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
